[
  {
    "startTime": 6.4,
    "endTime": 9.0,
    "text": "Hi, my name's Ed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.11,
    "endTime": 11.5,
    "text": "Welcome to Ed Explains English!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.51,
    "endTime": 18.25,
    "text": "With so much information being transferred nowadays, it's not surprising that some of it might get mixed up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.25,
    "endTime": 25.4,
    "text": "Therefore, it's necessary that we check with the people we are talking to, just to be sure that we've understood everything correctly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.5,
    "endTime": 28.5,
    "text": "Let's look at a few ways that we can do that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.06,
    "endTime": 33.0,
    "text": "Why don't we take a familiar situation at school, as an example?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.1,
    "endTime": 40.0,
    "text": "Your teacher has just explained something new to the class, so wants to get feedback from the students to check they've understood."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.1,
    "endTime": 44.0,
    "text": "These are the questions he or she could ask:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.1,
    "endTime": 46.0,
    "text": "'Do you understand?'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.1,
    "endTime": 49.0,
    "text": "'Are you following me?'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.1,
    "endTime": 53.0,
    "text": "'Do you understand what I mean?'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.1,
    "endTime": 56.0,
    "text": "'Do you understand what I'm saying?'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.1,
    "endTime": 58.0,
    "text": "'Any questions?'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.9,
    "endTime": 60.0,
    "text": "'Have you got it?'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.0,
    "endTime": 68.0,
    "text": "Now, there are two ways we can reply, either to express that we have understood:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.1,
    "endTime": 70.28899999999999,
    "text": "'Everything is comprehensible.'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.29,
    "endTime": 73.0,
    "text": "'Okay, I got what you mean.'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.58,
    "endTime": 75.48,
    "text": "'I understand what you mean.'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.48,
    "endTime": 78.0,
    "text": "'I see what you mean.'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.0,
    "endTime": 81.0,
    "text": "'I understand what you are saying.'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.0,
    "endTime": 83.0,
    "text": "'I've got it.'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.1,
    "endTime": 87.52,
    "text": "Or we need to use the following phrases if we have not understood:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.52,
    "endTime": 92.0,
    "text": "'Sorry, I didn't get your point.'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.1,
    "endTime": 93.78999999999999,
    "text": "'What do you mean?'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.79,
    "endTime": 98.0,
    "text": "'I'm not sure I got your point.'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.1,
    "endTime": 102.0,
    "text": "'I beg your pardon, but I don't quite understand.'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.1,
    "endTime": 104.78,
    "text": "'I don't quite follow you.'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.78,
    "endTime": 106.5,
    "text": "'I'm sorry.'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.51,
    "endTime": 110.0,
    "text": "'I don't understand what you mean.'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.5,
    "endTime": 118.0,
    "text": "Sometimes we think that we have understood, but might want to ask a question to check:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.1,
    "endTime": 122.0,
    "text": "'Could you clarify that please?'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.1,
    "endTime": 125.5,
    "text": "'Could you explain that please?'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.6,
    "endTime": 129.0,
    "text": "'What do you mean by that?'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.1,
    "endTime": 131.0,
    "text": "'Could you say that again?'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.1,
    "endTime": 134.0,
    "text": "'Could you repeat please?'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.1,
    "endTime": 137.0,
    "text": "'Could you put it differently please?'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.0,
    "endTime": 144.859,
    "text": "Our teacher will of course happily clarify the point he or she was making, by saying:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.0,
    "endTime": 150.0,
    "text": "'Sorry, let me explain.'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.1,
    "endTime": 153.5,
    "text": "'Let me clarify it for you.'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.6,
    "endTime": 157.0,
    "text": "'To put it differently.'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.1,
    "endTime": 159.5,
    "text": "'Let me put it another way.'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.0,
    "endTime": 163.0,
    "text": "'I will paraphrase that for you.'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.03,
    "endTime": 170.0,
    "text": "So, don't feel discouraged when you don't understand everything the first time around."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.8,
    "endTime": 175.0,
    "text": "Just think of these phrases and you'll be able to check you have understood, in no time at all."
  }
]